    "description": "Sharp Wands - WIP<br><br>Sharp wands, lets you fight your friends in a couch-coop experience with multiple playable characters, different game modes fully customizable, statuses and many obstacles to avoid and use at your own advantage!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2 - 4 Players local multiplayer<br></li><li> 4 different characters to play each with its own custom statistics and colors<br></li><li> Customization system to make the game exactly as you want to play it<br></li><li> Status effects for each map<br></li><li> Plenty of unique obstacles<br></li><li> Flexible team option allowing also to gang up on that annoying strong friend 😉<br></li><li> 3 different game modes: Deathmatch, Hold the Flag, Last Hit<br></li><li> 40 maps to play</li></ul><br>Each character has a common move-set, which includes <strong>combo melee</strong>, <strong>charged melee</strong>, <strong>combo ranged</strong>, <strong>charged ranged</strong> and <strong>guard</strong>. <br><br>There are currently 2 different game modes: Deathmatch and Capture the Flag. Each mode has a set of parameters that improve replayability by changing the match parameters such as rounds, duration, score target... With 3+ players there is also the option to set teams. Team up and support each other to win the game! Every team combination is valid: 1v3, 2v2<br><br>Each game is fully customizable so you can play whatever game you prefer. You might choose to play short and intense matches, or you may prefer a longer and strategic approach, the choice is yours!",
